    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">每回合1次：</span>如果手牌中沒有<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">聖俗雜座</span>，則生成手牌<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">聖俗雜座</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/26b9736a2d14fc4162b2448963f45695_3189507405759314015.png",
                "id": "talent39015",
                "key": "獨舞之邀",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "獨舞之邀"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">芙寧娜</span>目前處於「始基力：荒性」形態：召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">沙龍成員</span>。</p><p>（芙寧娜處於「始基力：芒性」形態時，會改為召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">眾水的歌者</span>）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/47e3b8a03c0e9406c19655e1aa7c3b30_6893842599396811086.png",
                "id": "talent95037",
                "key": "孤心沙龍",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "孤心沙龍"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素傷害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">普世歡騰</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">普世歡騰</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方出戰角色受到傷害或治療後：</span>疊加1點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">狂歡值</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/e5d9f5e8170236ccfb246be6a8bee57f_6483212015140670706.png",
                "id": "talent12711",
                "key": "萬眾狂歡",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "萬眾狂歡"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被動技能</span></p><p>【被動】戰鬥開始時，生成手牌<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">聖俗雜座</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/be37947534ecad684025e9577469afa4_1337907851932360048.png",
                "id": "talent2928",
                "key": "始基力：聖俗雜座",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "始基力：聖俗雜座"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素傷害</span>。如果我方存在生命值至少為6的角色，則對一位受傷最少的我方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span>，然後再造成1點<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span>（可疊加，最多疊加到4次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_4190893256575450206.png",
                "id": "talent85531",
                "key": "沙龍成員",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/742ece024b8fa2d5c64bdb5a98710fb7_6295947506356161833.png",
                "title": "沙龍成員"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>治療所有我方角色1點。如果我方存在生命值不多於5的角色，則再治療一位受傷最多的角色1點。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span>（可疊加，最多疊加到4次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7185220742456947384.png",
                "id": "talent58145",
                "key": "眾水的歌者",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/d87cb48ac9ce6214f901cfb7aa5cc542_4679809587406913751.png",
                "title": "眾水的歌者"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">事件牌</span></p><p>在「始基力：荒性」和「始基力：芒性」之中，切換芙寧娜的形態。</p><p>如果我方場上存在<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">沙龍成員</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">眾水的歌者</span>，也切換其形態。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_4872763434199123857.png",
                "id": "talent75978",
                "key": "聖俗雜座",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/b4812801014e3b4dfaed86c27639933c_6962148078726349539.png",
                "title": "聖俗雜座"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>傷害后提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綻放</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>傷害+2的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「草原核」</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_7855806766131427600.png",
                "id": "talent33960",
                "key": "水元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持續回合</span></p><p>每回合結束階段，<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">狂歡值</span></p><p>我方造成的傷害+1。（包括角色引發的擴散傷害）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span>（可疊加，沒有上限）</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>穿透傷害無法受到傷害加成，但是也無法被護盾、傷害免疫等效果抵消。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_8200203352305665219.png",
                "id": "talent47632",
                "key": "規則解釋",
